    "attributes": {
        "action": "Priority evacuation of families of Afghans who worked with British forces ",
        "additional_details": "There are reports these people are having to cheat death by hiding indoors with no money and no food, they are so scared to go out. These people are at risk, and nobody seems to be prioritising them or their families.",
        "background": "The Afghan families of people who worked with British forces and are already in the UK, including interpreters, must be evacuated from Afghanistan as a priority, either under the ARAP or the new ACRS scheme.",
